snippet.title: K-razy Shoot-Out (Atari 5200)
snippet.description:
Initial release date: 1981
Developer: K-Byte
Genre: Shoot 'em up
Platforms: Atari 8-bit family, Atari 5200
Publishers: K-Byte, CBS Electronics, CBS Interactive, CBS Software

if you want to support my channel, please consider becoming a member: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChFEtlcXm3fjuSIow_DX7Lg/join

when you're a member, these are the benefits you will have:
- your channel name and link in the description of new videos (shout-out)
- badges, icons that indicate you're a member and changes color after a certain amount of time (new=green, 1 month=blue, 2 months=yellow, 6 months=orange, 1 year=pink, 2 years=red)
- emojis that relate to the channel you can use in any comment you post on my videos
